New scoreboard ad submission — <%= it.status %>

  Submitter: <%= it.submitter %> <<%= it.submitterEmail %>>
  Company:   <%= it.company %>
  Ad title:  <%= it.adTitle %>
  Team:      <%= it.team %>
  Placement: <%= it.placementLabel %>
  Amount:    <%= it.amount %>
  Payment:   <%= it.paymentMethod %>
  Ad ID:     <%= it.adId %>
<% if (it.notes) { %>  Notes:     <%= it.notes %>
<% } %>
